<br>
Sorry if this has been coverd here before.  I couldn't find anything that would help me.<br>
<br>
I am a bit of a noob, so I have no clue how to figure out what axes my level 43 shadowblade should order from a WC.  <br>
<br>
I want to learn how to figure out what I need, instead of being told &quot;hey, this is the best axe for you&quot;.  Is there such a guide?<br>
<br>
I would also like some reference on the differences between axes that can be player crafted.  I'm not sure if this makes sense to anyone out here, so please let me know if I need to clarify.  Thanks in advance.<br>
