Note that the cleaver and weighted bearded axe are only available in mithril and better materials.<br>
<br>
A weapon cons yellow when (DPS - 1.2) / 0.3 = level of character.<br>
<br>
I know a lot of people go with a double bladed axe/hand axe or double bladed axe/weighted bearded axe combo to maximize the haste effect of Left Axe.<br>
<br>
For a level 43 SB, I think it would depend on how much cash you got. If you got the cash, you may want to go for the arcanium weapons so you can grow into them.<br>
<br>
Also as a disclaimer, I don't play a zerker or SB so I can't speak with personal knowledge. I only know what I've read off boards like this one. I'd also like to point out that the only good shadowblade is a dead one, especially when I just skewered them on top of a wall and am kicking their lifeless corpse off the top.<br>
<br>
